{"tid":1626220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"星期日終極惡法和理非大遊行請求大家總動員救香港","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T10:27:57.000Z","uid":126142,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"91d51a4926be0e67302e73848b312002b6be2655","tid":1626220,"uid":126142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:12:44.000Z","msg":"已無退路，以和理非最大力量對極權作最後警告<br />\n<br />\n聽日可能冇港鐵，要預多d時間出去<br />\n<br />\n今晚大家自己區派傳單"},{"pid":"740c485976cbddec5300ba67e0d6fe6376cc3b03","tid":1626220,"uid":257293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:13:04.000Z","msg":"裝修有好多種<br />\n其實裝修可以裝成連儂牆<br />\n新聞出嘅圖可以贏到輿論<br />\n又可以target警世呢啲紅底中資<br />\n貼滿中共紅底黑社會嘅證據<br />\n佢哋要拆要清都要搞到一大輪，甚至清唔到等佢哋自己換玻璃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQkIOjsel3Yjc1B7cRnhIfagIvmR4f4aVTBnzK5PhcCs6SwzlwstlaxQaqELvb708RI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=6ff3cb4718a8dad53be9276dd33cad72&amp;oe=5E364A79\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQkIOjsel3Yjc1B7cRnhIfagIvmR4f4aVTBnzK5PhcCs6SwzlwstlaxQaqELvb708RI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D6ff3cb4718a8dad53be9276dd33cad72%26oe%3D5E364A79&h=7003ea3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eefeecadb57b039ccede6cca2a7e23ebd431dc03","tid":1626220,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:22:36.000Z","msg":"【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"d04acb465c8ed9747c56182d731dabbd0aa09f5e","tid":1626220,"uid":126142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:27:57.000Z","msg":"推推"}]}